						<summary>

						<p>This damaged inscription refers itself to the reign of <hi rend="bold">Tribhuvanamalladēva;</hi> but the date is lost. It seems to register a grant of land. The Jain teacher Bāḷachandra of the Dēsiga-<hi rend="italic">gaṇa</hi> and Postaka-<hi rend="italic">gachchha</hi> and the division <hi rend="bold">[Ka]riviḍi Thirty</hi> are mentioned.</p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
